Variable.0.Name: DT
Variable.0.Description: Sonic
Variable.0.Unit: Seconds/meter
Variable.1.Type: Sonic travel time
Variable.1.Name: DTS
Variable.1.Description: Shear sonic
Variable.1.Unit: Seconds/meter
